表格系统模块管理的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('SysProgramInfo')
and type = 'U')
drop table SysProgramInfo
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: SysProgramInfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table SysProgramInfo (
ID int identity(1,1),
ProgramID nvarchar(50) not null,
ProgramName nvarchar(50) null,
RequestURL nvarchar(50) null,
ClassID nvarchar(50) null,
OrderID varchar(50) not null constraint DF_ProgramInfo_OrderID default (1),
Locked char(1) null,
aDate datetime null constraint DF_ProgramInfo_aDate default getdate(),
mDate datetime null constraint DF_ProgramInfo_mDate default getdate(),
constraint PK_ProgramInfo primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
